title: [AnonDCX] NG-BOOK 2: The Complete Book on AngularJS 2 (Revision
description:
Hi Guys, 

I was looking for a copy of this book online and couldnt find one for free so I decided to buy it and share it via torrents so anyone else in the same situation or anyone who cant afford it but really wants to learn can have it for free. 

Please if you do have the money and can afford it please do purchase the book as the developers need the funding to continue to make educational books for all of us. 

This is revision 38. 

Code samples are included and books formats are in MOBI, PDF and EPUB 

You can purchase it here: https://www.ng-book.com/2/ 

Changelog: https://www.ng-book.com/2/p/Changelog/
